to see you put away, you know?

70
00:08:12,294 --> 00:08:15,758
Yeah, wouldn't you think
there are better things to do?

71
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,902
You on your
own tonight?

72
00:08:16,903 --> 00:08:18,016
Why don't you come
round for dinner?

73
